author: Xbox
description:
ANNIE: Last Hope is a HD Voxel top-down shooter set in the 1990s. Following an apocalyptic outbreak of unknown creatures, a couple is separated in the chaos. Players take on the role of Annie, the protagonist, as she embarks on a perilous journey to find her missing fiancé, unaware that her path is fraught with deadly traps and unfolding calamity.
